#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:1
msgid "Primitive 原语系统"
msgstr "Primitive System"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:3
msgid ""
"Primitive 是 SimpleLLMFunc 的“运行时内置能力”（CodeAct 范式下的 builtin tool）。 它不是直接暴露给模型的"
" `@tool`，而是通过 `PyRepl` 的 `execute_code` 间接调用："
msgstr ""
"Primitive is SimpleLLMFunc's \"runtime built-in capability\" (builtin tool "
"under the CodeAct paradigm). It is not directly exposed to the model as "
"`@tool`, but is indirectly called via `PyRepl`'s `execute_code`:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:10
msgid "定位与作用"
msgstr "Positioning and Role"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:12
msgid ""
"在 CodeAct 模式下，模型会使用 `execute_code` 来执行一段 Python 代码。 Primitive "
"就是这段代码里可直接调用的“运行时 API”，例如："
msgstr ""
"In CodeAct mode, the model uses `execute_code` to execute a piece of Python "
"code. Primitive refers to the \"runtime API\" that can be directly called "
"within this code, for example:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:20
msgid "因此 Primitive 的定位是："
msgstr "Therefore, the positioning of Primitive is:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:22
msgid "**运行时能力入口**：不需要 import，直接从 `runtime` 命名空间访问"
msgstr ""
"**Runtime Capability Entry Point**: No import required, directly access from"
" the `runtime` namespace"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:23
msgid "**CodeAct 内置工具**：由 `PyRepl` 托管并运行"
msgstr "**CodeAct built-in tools**: hosted and run by `PyRepl`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:24
msgid ""
"**可被 LLM 发现和理解**：支持 `runtime.get_primitive_spec(...)` 与 "
"`runtime.list_primitive_specs(...)`"
msgstr ""
"**Discoverable and understandable by LLM**: supports "
"`runtime.get_primitive_spec(...)` and `runtime.list_primitive_specs(...)`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:26
msgid "关键概念"
msgstr "Key Concepts"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:28
msgid "PrimitivePack"
msgstr "PrimitivePack"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:30
msgid "PrimitivePack 是一组 runtime 原语的命名空间："
msgstr "PrimitivePack is a namespace for a set of runtime primitives:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:32
msgid "pack 名称决定 runtime 前缀：`runtime.<pack_name>.<primitive_name>`"
msgstr ""
"The pack name determines the runtime prefix: "
"`runtime.<pack_name>.<primitive_name>`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:33
msgid "pack 同时绑定一个默认 backend（见下文）"
msgstr "pack also binds a default backend (see below)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:34
msgid "pack 还可以带一个 `guidance` 字符串，用来描述这个 pack 的心智模型、典型用途与使用边界"
msgstr ""
"pack can also take a `guidance` string, which is used to describe this "
"pack's mental model, typical usage, and usage boundaries"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:35
msgid ""
"这个 `guidance` 会进入 `execute_code` 的 runtime primitive "
"contract，帮助模型先理解“这包能力是做什么的”"
msgstr ""
"This `guidance` will enter the `execute_code` runtime primitive contract, "
"helping the model first understand \"what this capability package is for\""

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:36
msgid ""
"具体到某个 primitive 的输入输出、参数与解析规则，仍然以 `runtime.get_primitive_spec(name)` / "
"`runtime.list_primitive_specs(...)` 为准"
msgstr ""
"For the input/output, parameters, and parsing rules of a specific primitive,"
" please refer to `runtime.get_primitive_spec(name)` / "
"`runtime.list_primitive_specs(...)`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:38
msgid "Primitive"
msgstr "Primitive"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:40
msgid "Primitive 是 pack 下面的一个运行时函数入口："
msgstr "Primitive is a runtime function entry point under pack:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:46
msgid "Primitive 的实现就是一个普通 Python 函数，但它会接收一个注入的上下文 `PrimitiveCallContext`。"
msgstr ""
"A Primitive implementation is just a regular Python function, but it "
"receives an injected context `PrimitiveCallContext`."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:48
msgid "Backend"
msgstr "Backend"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:50
msgid "Backend 是提供能力的 Python 对象（可选但推荐）："
msgstr ""
"Backend is a capability-providing Python object (optional but recommended):"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:52
msgid "可以是 dict / service / client / 自定义类实例"
msgstr "can be dict / service / client / custom class instance"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:53
msgid "用来承载状态或真实能力"
msgstr "used to carry state or real capabilities"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:54
msgid "通过 `ctx.backend` 或 `ctx.get_backend(...)` 注入到 primitive handler"
msgstr ""
"Injected into primitive handler via `ctx.backend` or `ctx.get_backend(...)`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:55
msgid "有 fork / 安装 / 关闭生命周期需求时，建议实现 `RuntimePrimitiveBackend`"
msgstr ""
"When there are fork / install / shutdown lifecycle requirements, it is "
"recommended to implement `RuntimePrimitiveBackend`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:57
msgid "开发流程（推荐写法）"
msgstr "Development Process (Recommended)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:59
msgid "最推荐的 authoring / registration 路径是："
msgstr "The most recommended authoring / registration path is:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:61
msgid "`repl.pack(name, backend=..., guidance=\"...\")`"
msgstr "repl.pack(name, backend=..., guidance=\"...\")"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:62
msgid "`@pack.primitive(...)`"
msgstr "`@pack.primitive(...)`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:63
msgid "`repl.install_pack(pack)`"
msgstr "`repl.install_pack(pack)`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:65
msgid "这条路径最适合需要命名空间、共享 backend、pack 级 guidance 和 fork 生命周期控制的 runtime 扩展。"
msgstr ""
"This path is best suited for runtime extensions that require namespace, "
"shared backend, pack-level guidance, and fork lifecycle control."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:120
msgid "如果只是轻量扩展，也可以使用 `@repl.primitive(...)`："
msgstr ""
"If it's just a lightweight extension, you can also use "
"`@repl.primitive(...)`:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:136
msgid ""
"如果你在做更底层的宿主集成，也可以直接使用 `PrimitiveRegistry.register(...)`。 不过对大多数使用 `PyRepl` "
"的场景来说，优先推荐 `PrimitivePack` 路径，因为它天然把 namespace、backend、guidance "
"和安装生命周期放在同一个抽象里。"
msgstr ""
"If you're doing lower-level host integration, you can also directly use "
"`PrimitiveRegistry.register(...)`. However, for most `PyRepl` usage "
"scenarios, the `PrimitivePack` path is recommended, as it naturally "
"encapsulates namespace, backend, guidance, and installation lifecycle within"
" the same abstraction."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:139
msgid "在哪里被使用"
msgstr "Where is it used"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:141
msgid "`PyRepl.execute_code`：运行时环境里提供 `runtime.*` 命名空间"
msgstr ""
"`PyRepl.execute_code`: the runtime environment provides the `runtime.*` "
"namespace"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:142
msgid "`llm_chat(toolkit=repl.toolset)`：模型调用 `execute_code` 后，才能访问 primitives"
msgstr ""
"`llm_chat(toolkit=repl.toolset)`: The model can only access primitives after"
" calling `execute_code`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:143
msgid ""
"内置 selfref pack：`runtime.selfref.history.*` / "
"`runtime.selfref.fork.*`，同样通过包级 `guidance` 向模型提供命名空间心智模型"
msgstr ""
"Built-in selfref pack: `runtime.selfref.history.*` / "
"`runtime.selfref.fork.*`, also providing a namespace mental model to the "
"model through package-level `guidance`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:145
msgid "Primitive 上下文注入"
msgstr "Primitive context injection"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:147
msgid "每个 primitive handler 都会收到 `PrimitiveCallContext`，包含："
msgstr "Each primitive handler receives `PrimitiveCallContext`, containing:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:149
msgid "`primitive_name`：当前 primitive 的完整名称"
msgstr "`primitive_name`: the full name of the current primitive"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:150
msgid "`call_id` / `execution_id`：执行链路标识"
msgstr "`call_id` / `execution_id`: execution chain identifier"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:151
msgid "`event_emitter`：可用于发送自定义事件"
msgstr "`event_emitter`: can be used to send custom events"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:152
msgid "`repl` / `registry`：运行时宿主与注册中心"
msgstr "`repl` / `registry`: Runtime Host and Registry"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:153
msgid "`backend_name`：当前 primitive 默认绑定的 backend 名"
msgstr ""
"`backend_name`: the name of the default backend bound to the current "
"primitive"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:154
msgid "`backend`：通过 backend_name 注入的 backend 对象"
msgstr "\"backend\": the backend object injected via backend_name"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:156
msgid "上下文的注入流程："
msgstr "Context injection process:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:163
msgid ""
"因此建议：**primitive handler 优先通过 `ctx.backend` / `ctx.get_backend(...)` 访问能力**。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore recommended: **primitive handler preferably accesses capabilities "
"via `ctx.backend` / `ctx.get_backend(...)`**."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:165
msgid "Contract 与可发现性"
msgstr "Contract and Discoverability"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:167
msgid "Primitive 支持结构化契约，用于模型发现："
msgstr "Primitive supports structured contracts for model discovery:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:169
msgid "`runtime.get_primitive_spec(name)`：单条契约"
msgstr "`runtime.get_primitive_spec(name)`: single contract"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:170
msgid "`runtime.list_primitive_specs(...)`：批量契约"
msgstr "runtime.list_primitive_specs(...): batch contract"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:172
msgid "默认格式为 XML，也可使用 `format='dict'` 返回结构化字段。 契约信息来自以下来源："
msgstr ""
"The default format is XML. You can also use `format='dict'` to return structured fields.\n"
"Contract information comes from the following sources:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:175
msgid "handler 的 docstring（Use/Input/Output/Parse/Parameters/Best Practices）"
msgstr ""
"handler's docstring (Use/Input/Output/Parse/Parameters/Best Practices)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:176
msgid "`PrimitiveContract` / `@primitive(...)` 装饰器显式参数"
msgstr "`PrimitiveContract` / `@primitive(...)` decorator explicit parameters"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:178
msgid "PrimitiveContract vs PrimitiveSpec"
msgstr "PrimitiveContract vs PrimitiveSpec"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:180
msgid ""
"`PrimitiveContract`：author-side 的契约定义，描述 primitive 的输入输出、参数、解析方式与 next steps"
msgstr ""
"PrimitiveContract: author-side contract definition, describing the "
"primitive's input/output, parameters, parsing method, and next steps"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:181
msgid ""
"`PrimitiveSpec`：runtime/public 侧看到的最终 spec，已经带上注册名、backend 绑定与归一化后的 contract"
" 字段"
msgstr ""
"`PrimitiveSpec`: the final spec seen from the runtime/public side, already "
"carrying the registration name, backend binding, and normalized contract "
"fields"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:183
msgid "可以把它们理解为："
msgstr "They can be understood as:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:185
msgid "`PrimitiveContract` = 你在“定义 primitive”时写进去的结构化声明"
msgstr ""
"`PrimitiveContract` = The structured declaration you wrote when \"defining "
"primitive\""

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:186
msgid "`PrimitiveSpec` = 模型和运行时在“读取 primitive”时看到的最终公开说明"
msgstr ""
"`PrimitiveSpec` = The final public specification seen by the model and "
"runtime when \"reading a primitive\""

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:188
msgid "字段解析顺序是："
msgstr "Field parsing order is:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:190
msgid ""
"`description` / `input_type` / `output_type` / `output_parsing`：显式参数 > "
"`PrimitiveContract` > docstring"
msgstr ""
"`description` / `input_type` / `output_type` / `output_parsing`: explicit "
"parameter > `PrimitiveContract` > docstring"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:191
msgid "`parameters`：显式参数 > `PrimitiveContract` > docstring > 签名推断"
msgstr ""
"`parameters`：explicit parameters > `PrimitiveContract` > docstring > "
"signature inference"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:192
msgid "`next_steps`：显式参数 > `PrimitiveContract` > docstring"
msgstr "`next_steps`: explicit parameter > `PrimitiveContract` > docstring"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:193
msgid "`best_practices`：来自 docstring，并且为必填项"
msgstr "`best_practices`: from docstring, and is a required field"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:195
msgid "因此最稳妥的写法是："
msgstr "Therefore, the safest approach is:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:197
msgid ""
"在 docstring 中完整写出 `Use` / `Input` / `Output` / `Parse` / `Parameters` / "
"`Best Practices`"
msgstr ""
"In the docstring, fully write out `Use` / `Input` / `Output` / `Parse` / "
"`Parameters` / `Best Practices`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:198
msgid "在确实需要覆盖或程序化生成字段时，再使用 `PrimitiveContract` 或 `@primitive(...)` 的显式参数"
msgstr ""
"Only use the explicit parameters of `PrimitiveContract` or `@primitive(...)`"
" when you really need to override or programmatically generate fields"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:200
msgid "Best Practices 与 Docstring"
msgstr "Best Practices and Docstring"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:202
msgid ""
"Primitive 的最佳实践 **只来自 docstring**，且为必填项。 缺失 `Best Practices` 会在注册时抛出错误。"
msgstr ""
"The Best Practices for Primitive **only come from docstring**, and it is a "
"required field. Missing `Best Practices` will throw an error during "
"registration."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:205
msgid "Docstring 结构规范"
msgstr "Docstring Structure Specification"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:207
msgid "Docstring 采用“段落 + 冒号”的简洁格式，大小写不敏感："
msgstr "Docstring uses the simple \"paragraph + colon\" format, case insensitive:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:209
msgid "`Use:` / `Input:` / `Output:` / `Parse:`"
msgstr "Use: / Input: / Output: / Parse:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:210
msgid "`Parameters:`（每行 `name: description` 或 `- name: description`）"
msgstr "Parameters: (each line `name: description` or `- name: description`)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:211
msgid "`Best Practices:`（每行 `- rule`）"
msgstr ""
"Best Practices:\n"
"(each line `- rule`)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:213
msgid "没有标题的首段会自动当作 `Use`（description）。"
msgstr ""
"The first paragraph without a title will automatically be treated as `Use` "
"(description)."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:215
msgid "推荐的完整模板："
msgstr "Recommended complete template:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:234
msgid "**提示**：Best Practices 依赖 docstring 解析，请把规则写在 docstring。"
msgstr ""
"**Note**: Best Practices relies on docstring parsing, please write the rules"
" in the docstring."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:236
msgid "这些最佳实践会进入 primitive contract，可以通过："
msgstr ""
"These best practices will go into the primitive contract, which can be "
"accessed through:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:238
msgid "`runtime.get_primitive_spec(\"github_repo.list_open_issues\")`"
msgstr "`runtime.get_primitive_spec(\"github_repo.list_open_issues\")`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:239
msgid "`runtime.list_primitive_specs(contains=\"github_repo.\")`"
msgstr "`runtime.list_primitive_specs(contains=\"github_repo.\")`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:241
msgid "来读取。"
msgstr "to read"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:243
msgid "如何注入到提示词里"
msgstr "How to inject into the prompt"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:245
msgid "Primitive **本身不会直接注入 system prompt**。"
msgstr "Primitive **itself does not directly inject into system prompt**"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:247
msgid "系统会注入的是 **工具（Tool）的最佳实践**，例如 `execute_code` 工具："
msgstr ""
"The system will inject **best practices for tools (Tool)**, for example the "
"`execute_code` tool:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:249
msgid ""
"`llm_chat` / `llm_function` 会把工具的 `best_practices` 去重后拼成 "
"`<tool_best_practices>` 块"
msgstr ""
"`llm_chat` / `llm_function` will deduplicate the tool's `best_practices` and"
" combine them into a `<tool_best_practices>` block"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:250
msgid "这块内容被插入到 system prompt 顶部"
msgstr "This content is inserted at the top of the system prompt"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:252
msgid "因此 Primitive 的最佳实践通常通过两种方式“进入模型上下文”："
msgstr ""
"Thus, Primitive's best practices typically \"enter the model context\" in "
"two ways:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:254
msgid "**execute_code 工具最佳实践**：提示模型使用 `runtime.get_primitive_spec(...)`"
msgstr ""
"**execute_code Tool Best Practices**: Instruct the model to use "
"`runtime.get_primitive_spec(...)`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:255
msgid ""
"**运行时主动查询**：模型在 `execute_code` 中调用 `runtime.get_primitive_spec` 或 "
"`runtime.selfref.guide()`"
msgstr ""
"**Runtime Active Query**: The model calls `runtime.get_primitive_spec` or "
"`runtime.selfref.guide()` in `execute_code`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:257
msgid "如果你希望把某个 primitive 的规则“强注入提示词”，建议把规则写到："
msgstr ""
"If you want to \"strongly inject\" the rules of a primitive into prompts, it"
" is recommended to write the rules to:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:259
msgid "`execute_code` 工具的 best practices（或自定义 Tool）"
msgstr "`execute_code` tool's best practices (or custom Tool)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:260
msgid "或通过 tool 的 `prompt_injection_builder` 输出固定指导文本"
msgstr ""
"or output fixed guidance text through tool's `prompt_injection_builder`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:262
msgid "Backend 生命周期与 fork/clone"
msgstr "Backend lifecycle and fork/clone"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:264
msgid "如果 backend 有状态，建议实现 `RuntimePrimitiveBackend`："
msgstr ""
"If the backend has state, it is recommended to implement "
"`RuntimePrimitiveBackend`:"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:266
msgid "`clone_for_fork(context=...)`：fork child 时如何复制/共享 backend（默认共享）"
msgstr ""
"`clone_for_fork(context=...)`: how to copy/share backend when forking child "
"(default: share)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:267
msgid "`on_install(repl)`：安装时回调"
msgstr "`on_install(repl)`: install callback"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:268
msgid "`on_close(repl)`：REPL 关闭时回调（可做资源释放）"
msgstr "`on_close(repl)`: callback when REPL closes (can do resource release)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:270
msgid "这让 fork 子 agent 时的 backend 行为更可控，也能保证状态清理。"
msgstr ""
"This makes the backend behavior more controllable when forking child agents,"
" and also ensures state cleanup."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:272
msgid "Primitive vs Tool"
msgstr "Primitive vs Tool"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:274
msgid "**Tool**：`@tool` 暴露给模型的函数调用（OpenAI tool calling）"
msgstr ""
"**Tool**: `@tool` function call exposed to the model (OpenAI tool calling)"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:275
msgid "**Primitive**：CodeAct 运行时内置 API，通过 `execute_code` 间接调用"
msgstr ""
"**Primitive**: CodeAct runtime built-in API, called indirectly via "
"`execute_code`"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/primitive.md:277
msgid "你可以把 Primitive 理解为“内置在运行时的 builtin tool”。"
msgstr "You can think of Primitive as a \"builtin tool built into the runtime\"."
